a.org/resource/Kohler_Co.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time was the third-best among the 30 competitors.\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She got off the line slowly, but passed Austria's Magdalena Lobnig in the back half of the race to pull away with a 6.93-second victory.\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4834, \"end\": 4841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999982125848477, \"rank\": 1.7874182106143151e-06, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4844, \"end\": 4860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magdalena_Lobnig\", \"score\": 0.9999982376027288, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Magdalena Lobnig\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magdalena_Lobnig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magdalena_Lobnig\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely a confidence boost, so I wanted to go out and have a solid race to have some confidence moving forward,\\\"Kohler told U.S. Rowing.\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 5077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5053, \"end\": 5059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kohler_Co.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.743361907334146e-16, \"text\": \"Kohler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kohler_Co.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kohler_Co.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely good to let her rip out there.\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each race is going to be more intense with a lot more on the line, so I think staying present and remembering how to row with all the excitement and adrenaline is the big thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 5126, \"t